{
  "texts": [
    "As such, our research project revolved around separate, yet complementary research questions and analyses:",
    "RQ1: What hinders (responsible) digital health innovation?",
    "RQ2: What are innovation and governance best-practices to advance responsible digital health innovation?",
    "We presented a detailed account of the preliminary study results for RQ1 in a separate study 54.",
    "This paper presents the results of our stakeholder engagement and corresponding analyses for RQ 2."
  ]
}